TITLE: Using mapInput with apiato Request (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the `mapInput` helper method on an apiato request object. It takes an associative array where keys are the current field paths (dot notation) and values are the desired new field paths. This modifies the request's internal data for streamlined processing by subsequent tasks or actions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apiato/documentation/blob/master/versioned_docs/version-9.x/main-components/requests.md#_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: php
