DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the usage of a transformer from within a controller to transform a user object.  It takes a user object and transforms it using `UserTransformer::class`.  It requires the `UserTransformer` class, and the `getUser()` method is assumed to be available in the controller. The expected output is a transformed user object in the API response.
