TITLE: Defining Validation Rules in Apiato Request (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to define validation rules within an Apiato Request class. The `rules()` method returns an array where keys are field names and values are Laravel validation rule strings. This example sets rules for email, password, and name fields for a user registration request.
