TITLE: Defining an Apiato Update User Request (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: Example of a concrete Request class (`UpdateUserRequest`) in Apiato extending `App\Ship\Parents\Requests\Request`. It defines access control via the `$access` property, validation rules in the `rules()` method, and authorization logic in the `authorize()` method using the `check()` helper with `hasAccess` and `isOwner` functions.
