TITLE: Event/Listener Registration Flow Diagram (mermaid)
DESCRIPTION: A visual diagram using Mermaid syntax illustrating the flow of how service providers, including event service providers, are loaded by the application's Service Provider Loader and how events and listeners are registered within them.
